Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您這是幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑…快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  你們以為跑得掉嗎？
